{"tid":2262883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"玫瑰崗撤教職員解僱安排","createTime":"2020-10-29T12:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T12:44:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3a71fca606f842b4a2da3760ea89aa20359e74d","tid":2262883,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/CSPO77466BHTZPGSJBZJEKOAZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FCSPO77466BHTZPGSJBZJEKOAZQ%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=d40d047b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FCSPO77466BHTZPGSJBZJEKOAZQ%2F&h=44322d3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/CSPO77466BHTZPGSJBZJEKOAZQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n玫瑰崗撤教職員解僱安排<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sqXuN1iTXfbWcDbXGyre95kdNos=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GUEKJF4DQ5DZZECP7TNP4CGS3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsqXuN1iTXfbWcDbXGyre95kdNos%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGUEKJF4DQ5DZZECP7TNP4CGS3Y.jpg&h=503e00fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■玫瑰崗幼稚園及小學部解僱教職員風波已暫告一段落。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】司徒拔道玫瑰崗幼稚園及小學部解僱教職員風波暫告一段落，校方承諾擱置有關解僱安排。該校校監何幼孫本周一發出通告，就事件引起各持份者不安致歉，又稱受武肺疫情影響，學校承受沉重財政壓力，將檢討今次事件處理方法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n承諾訂合理機制處理人手<br />\n<br />\n何稱校方早前解僱數名教師引起家長及校友關注，審慎考慮各持份者意見後撤回該決定，並承諾本學年會透過資源調配，維持現有人手安排。何又承諾若日後有必要重整人手，管理層必定及早與教師及職員代表商討，共同訂定公平及合理。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n該校上周五突裁走幼稚園部11名教職員，小學部則有5名教師被裁，當中有人年。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6c3d92f44635a64d196bb90d693ab965126d1713","tid":2262883,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"炒個人都做唔到 為官避事"},{"pid":"a480c2d1e08928b09b2cef432ac980e344818c23","tid":2262883,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"財政壓力？學生無俾學費？"},{"pid":"1d09c355d71082eb19a182059111d54faea91a3a","tid":2262883,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"換自己友入去"},{"pid":"4e969b8df153c1fd370fdc9eddb1fe37be0a8b54","tid":2262883,"uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"起碼肯聽意見呀"},{"pid":"bee81eb426981f559dbd04912c96c2599758b9df","tid":2262883,"uid":60527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n學校有咩財政壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學費又照收"},{"pid":"78ad3da53e0da686970e0c4fac03ffe986ce5ce8","tid":2262883,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bee81eb426981f559dbd04912c96c2599758b9df","tid":2262883,"uid":60527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n學校有咩財政壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學費又照收"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}